            "enName": "Matikanefukukitaru",
            "jpText": "――それにしても、珍しいですねぇ。\nスズカさんが他の方のレースを\n観たがるだなんて。",
            "enText": "I must say, it's rare isn't it, for you to \ncome watch somebody else's race.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "voiceIdx": 52,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": -2962060908324162180
