            "enText": "…I felt that there was a reason why I \nhad to come see today's Satsuki Sho.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 3593434521705216819
